    "attributes": {
        "action": "Abolish compulsory jury service for those over state pension age",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Allow all pensioners the option of whether or not they attend jury service. After all the UK population is growing at a steady pace thus creating a larger pool of working age individuals to be called upon. Let pensioners enjoy their retirement.",
